.DT
test_save
Disk World creator help
test_save

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
test_save -  This method determines if a given object should be saved or not.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int test_save(object ob)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^ob%^RESET%^ - The object to be tested.
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 for yes 0 for no.
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/room/inherit/room_save.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method determines if a given object should be saved or not.  When
inheriting this room you should define your own test_save function and use
it to decide which parts of the inventory are saved and which are not.

.EP

